description: APPLICATION FOR A CERTIFICATE OF LAWFULNESS TO CONFIRM THAT FLATS B1-B6, C1-C6, D1-D9, E1-E9, F1-F9, G1-G9, H1-H9, J1-J6 AND K1-K9 FALL UNDER RESIDENTIAL (CLASS C3) USE.
decision_conditions: Condition : 1 - The Local Planning Authority is satisfied that at the time the application was made, residential use (C3 Use Class) had been subsisting at Flat Nos. B1-B6, C1-C6, D1-D9, E1-E9, F1-F9, G1-G9, H1-H9, J1-J6 and K1-K9, as shown on the approved site location plan, for a period of no less than 10 years ending with the date of the application.
